37:02.210 --> 37:04.180
Ho, ho, ho!

37:04.180 --> 37:06.710
Merry Christmas,
Hope!

37:19.660 --> 37:22.660
This is the part
where you say something.

37:25.100 --> 37:27.840
Or run.

37:27.840 --> 37:29.340
It's both.

37:29.340 --> 37:31.670
Can you please
just wait right here?

37:31.670 --> 37:33.640
I have something that I
really need to tell you. I...

37:33.640 --> 37:35.380
I just can't until I've had

37:35.380 --> 37:37.810
another conversation first.

37:43.920 --> 37:46.550
Hey, Jo.

37:56.100 --> 37:58.700
Merry Christmas, I guess?

37:58.700 --> 38:01.770
You know what's weird
about Christmas?

38:01.770 --> 38:03.040
It's, um...

38:03.040 --> 38:05.740
the happiest and the saddest.

38:05.740 --> 38:08.710
Can we start with the happy?

38:08.710 --> 38:11.780
♪ And it's colder ♪

38:11.780 --> 38:13.950
♪ To turn on your side... ♪

38:13.950 --> 38:16.950
A person could not ask
for a better partner,

38:16.950 --> 38:20.090
a better conscience.

38:20.090 --> 38:21.660
♪ And I know you... ♪

38:21.660 --> 38:24.960
You are literally
the best person that's ever had

38:24.960 --> 38:26.790
the poor judgement
to hang out with me.

38:26.790 --> 38:29.700
♪ We didn't get tonight,
we don't have tomorrow... ♪

38:29.700 --> 38:31.270
I love the
way you laugh.

38:31.270 --> 38:33.230
♪ So don't ruin now... ♪

38:33.230 --> 38:36.670
And your upside down mouth.

38:36.670 --> 38:40.140
The way your face looks
when you watch movies and...

38:40.140 --> 38:42.240
You're in love with Hope.

38:42.240 --> 38:44.280
♪ How we gonna move ♪

38:44.280 --> 38:47.080
♪ Together ♪

38:47.080 --> 38:49.080
But that doesn't mean

38:49.080 --> 38:52.020
I regret a single second.

38:52.020 --> 38:54.290
♪ If we don't move... ♪

38:54.290 --> 38:56.020
Because you
are beautiful.

38:56.020 --> 38:58.230
♪ Together... ♪

38:58.230 --> 39:00.760
And special.

39:00.760 --> 39:04.270
And... perfect.

39:04.270 --> 39:07.770
♪ How we gonna breathe ♪

39:07.770 --> 39:09.970
♪ How we gonna be ♪

39:09.970 --> 39:13.340
And doing the right thing
should never be this hard.

39:26.020 --> 39:29.160
I thought leaving
was the right thing to do.

39:29.160 --> 39:31.160
♪ Everything's loud... ♪

39:31.160 --> 39:33.130
But I was wrong.

39:35.360 --> 39:39.070
That's what I came back to say.

39:40.300 --> 39:42.570
I love you, Hope Mikaelson.

39:42.570 --> 39:45.570
I-I loved you when I
couldn't remember you.

39:45.570 --> 39:48.180
I love you as I'm standing
here right now.

39:48.180 --> 39:51.350
Hope, I loved you
when I was dead.

39:51.350 --> 39:54.020
♪ The tiniest thing... ♪

39:54.020 --> 39:55.950
I think I always will.

39:57.090 --> 39:58.590
♪ But we didn't get tonight ♪

39:58.590 --> 40:01.160
♪ We don't have tomorrow ♪

40:01.160 --> 40:02.360
♪ So I'm done whispering... ♪

40:02.360 --> 40:03.390
This is the part
where you say...

40:03.390 --> 40:05.330
That I love you, too...

40:05.330 --> 40:08.860
Landon Kirby.

40:08.860 --> 40:11.830
God, I loved you
when you didn't even know it.

40:14.540 --> 40:17.340
Despite the way you've looked
in a football uniform.

40:17.340 --> 40:18.510
(laughing)

40:22.180 --> 40:24.010
♪ And let me say ♪

40:24.010 --> 40:26.350
♪ In the dark
of the morning... ♪

40:26.350 --> 40:28.950
Then there's only one thing
left to say.

40:28.950 --> 40:31.090
♪ Just one more thing... ♪

40:31.090 --> 40:32.890
Look up.

40:34.360 --> 40:36.360
♪ How we gonna move ♪

40:36.360 --> 40:38.330
♪ Together? ♪

40:38.330 --> 40:42.960
♪ Just come closer ♪

40:44.270 --> 40:47.170
♪ If we don't move ♪

40:47.170 --> 40:49.340
♪ Together ♪

40:52.170 --> 40:54.980
♪ Just keeping the peace ♪

40:57.680 --> 41:00.850
♪ Just keeping the peace. ♪

41:09.620 --> 41:11.290
Don't worry, Dad.

41:13.300 --> 41:15.260
I'll be home for Christmas.

